\[ \text{Earnings of Tiger Woods} > \text{Earnings of David Toms} \]

\[ 5,687,777 > 3,791,595 \]

Tiger Woods indeed earned more money overall than David Toms.

### Conclusion

- The first part of the claim ("tiger wood play 3 less event than david tom") is false because Tiger Woods played 9 fewer events, not 3.
- The second part of the claim ("but earn more money overall") is true because Tiger Woods earned more than David Toms.
